CoplingSearchHelpSearchChild:

CoplingSearchHelpSearchParent:
You can narrow your results by choosing

CoplingSearchHelpSearchStart:

CoplingSearchHelpSearchChildGenealogy:
Select the family you desire for the
monsters resulting from fusion.

Filter only the desired Rank of monsters
resulting from fusion.

that you've never seen before.
CoplingSearchHelpParentAll:
Search all fusions that can be created
using any monsters you've seen.
CoplingSearchHelpParentOwn:

using any monsters you have currently.
CoplingSearchHelpChildAll:
Search all candidates for fusion out
of only monsters that you have never
seen before.
